---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service — green°">
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-page__inner">

      <header class="legal-page__header">
        <span class="legal-page__eyebrow">legal</span>
        <h1 class="legal-page__title">Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="legal-page__updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>
      </header>

      <div class="legal-page__body">

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Who we are</h2>
          <p>green° is a Cape Town-based social enterprise and non-profit initiative founded in December 2019 by Anne and Cheryl. We hand-make bags and lifestyle products from rescued kites, denim, and parachutes, and use the proceeds to fund stationery packs for children at Western Cape primary schools.</p>
          <p>This website exists to share our story, let you browse our collections, and accept donations and product enquiries. By using the site you agree to these terms.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Products and purchases</h2>
          <p>Because every piece is made from rescued and donated materials, no two items are identical. Product descriptions and photos are as accurate as we can make them, but small variations in colour, texture, and finish are part of what makes each bag unique.</p>
          <p>For pricing and to place an order, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@greendegree.co.za">hello@greendegree.co.za</a>. South African consumer rights under the <strong>Consumer Protection Act 68 of 2008</strong> apply to all product sales — which means if something arrives faulty or not as described, we'll make it right.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Donations</h2>
          <p>Donation payments are processed securely by <a href="https://www.yoco.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yoco</a>, a South African payment provider. green° never stores or sees your card details — Yoco handles all of that.</p>
          <p>Because donations go directly towards purchasing stationery for school children, <strong>we are unable to offer refunds on donations</strong>. If a payment error occurs, please get in touch and we'll sort it out together.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
          <p>All text, photography, and design on this site belongs to green°. You're welcome to share our content on social media with credit, but please don't reproduce it commercially without asking us first.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Links to other sites</h2>
          <p>We link to third-party services including <a href="https://www.instagram.com/greendegree_/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram (@greendegree_)</a> and <a href="https://www.yoco.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Yoco</a> for payments. Once you leave our site, their own terms and privacy policies apply — we have no control over their content or practices.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Governing law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the Republic of South Africa. Any disputes will be dealt with in South African courts.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="legal-section">
          <h2>Questions?</h2>
          <p>If anything here is unclear, or you have a question about an order or donation, email us at <a href="mailto:hello@greendegree.co.za">hello@greendegree.co.za</a> and we'll get back to you as soon as we can.</p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding-top: 96px; /* clear the fixed nav */
    padding-bottom: 120px;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }

  .legal-page__inner {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding-inline: var(--page-pad);
  }

  /* ---- Header ---- */
  .legal-page__header {
    padding: 64px 0 56px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .legal-page__eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-sage-deep);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .legal-page__eyebrow::after {
    content: "";
    display: inline-block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-sage-deep);
  }

  .legal-page__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
    letter-spacing: -0.028em;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .legal-page__updated {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-ink-faint);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  /* ---- Body ---- */
  .legal-page__body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .legal-section {
    padding-bottom: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  }

  .legal-section:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.625rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.018em;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .legal-section p {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--color-ink-soft);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    max-width: 68ch;
  }

  .legal-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .legal-section a {
    color: var(--color-denim);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(61, 76, 102, 0.3);
    transition: border-color 160ms;
  }

  .legal-section a:hover {
    border-bottom-color: var(--color-denim);
  }

  /* ---- Mobile ---- */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .legal-page {
      padding-top: 72px;
      padding-bottom: 80px;
    }

    .legal-page__inner {
      padding-inline: var(--page-pad-mobile);
    }

    .legal-page__header {
      padding: 40px 0 40px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }

    .legal-section {
      padding-bottom: 36px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }
  }
</style>
